%div{ style: 'font-family: Arial,sans-serif; font-size:13px;' }
  %p{ style: 'margin: 0 0 1.6em 0;' }
    Hello there!

  - if @user.email == 'support@thrive.ly'
    %p{ style: 'margin: 0 0 1.6em 0;' }
      You've been invited to try the Thrively private beta.
      Sign up now to begin easily exchanging professional feedback with anyone
      with an email address.

    %p{ style: 'margin: 0 0 1.6em 0;' }
      = link_to "Click here to get started with Thrively.",
          accept_url(invite: @invite.token)

    %p{ style: 'margin: 0 0 1.6em 0;' }
      Thank you.

    %hr{ style: 'height: 1px; background-color: #ccc; color: #ccc; border: none; border: 0px solid #ccc;'}

    %p{ style: 'margin: 0 0 1.6em 0;' }
      Thrively is currently in our private beta test with a small group of users.
      Please contact us at #{Mailer::SUPPORT_ADDRESS} to share your thoughts and
      suggestions.

    %p{ style: 'margin: 0 0 1.6em 0;' }
      \© 2012 – Thrively, Inc., 474 55th Street, Unit B, Oakland, CA 94609, USA

  - else
    %p{ style: 'margin: 0 0 1.6em 0;' }
      #{@user.name} has invited you to try Thrively.
      Sign up now to begin easily exchanging professional feedback with anyone
      with an email address.

    %p{ style: 'margin: 0 0 1.6em 0;' }
      Click the link below to accept the invitation:

    %p{ style: 'margin: 0 0 1.6em 0;' }
      = link_to accept_url(invite: @invite.token),
          accept_url(invite: @invite.token)

    = render 'footer', sender_name: @user.name
